{"tid":1973872,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［開始分化黃媒］嚴重黑色五毛分化技倆 現在生效！！！","createTime":"2020-04-15T12:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T17:45:56.000Z","uid":70888,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f91b256fb733ca4fcd544916cbaed987067538c6","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"紅媒有 cctvb，大公，文匯，東方，01 等等太多<br />\n黃媒蘋果，立場，香港電台，仲有網媒<br />\n<br />\n要贏對家，首先要贏媒體既佔有率，就如cctvb普及每個人屋企 日播夜播奶共新聞，抹黑反送中抗爭同黃圈，係非常有影響力。<br />\n<br />\n五毛由黃圈youtuber內鬥分化<br />\n到依家開始分化黃媒<br />\n利用蘋果訂唔訂閱開始製造兩班黃絲互屌<br />\n其實真係好危險<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果少一間黃媒，就以蘋果為例，最開心既一定係中共</span>，亦會被紅媒大肆造遙 黃圈係少數派 頂唔住了，影響非常嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果一直被支那封殺，好多大公司都唔可以係蘋果落廣告，一直蝕住燒錢做，要走到訂閱相信係最後一步棋。<br />\n<br />\n黃圈就係大家有共同既理念抗爭，咁多紅媒可以生存到依家，就係中共不斷泵水比佢地，倒轉亦一樣，蘋果訂閱就係想大家幫手，我地黃圈係需要互相support，由學生，醫護，黃店，到媒體 真係需要大家幫助。<br />\n<br />\n你可以搵到唔同理由挑剔蘋果既問題而唔訂閱，但到無左一間黃媒既時候，黃媒既佔有率同影響力就會大大減低。而學cctvb咁講中共就係贏家。<br />\n<br />\n依家大家可以選擇比錢撐黃媒為我地發聲，但遲下 可能未到2047年，中共可能已經完全封殺晒黃媒，到時想用錢去買一把為我地黃圈出聲既聲音都無，只係想講 好好珍惜 每一位黃絲 黃店 黃公司。<br />\n唔好再分化同批判黃圈，對家食住花生望住我地。"},{"pid":"f65c11022cc241959d62e485879071462fa35c15","tid":1973872,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4134cfe4c06e68d661b9201f4d94d44368e6ed59","tid":1973872,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8563d873742cf232857ea723290e18a014bcad43","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"大家試下代入對家，再望下我地依家既黃圈，依家就係佢地最期待既畫面了"},{"pid":"81ebebe1c3204eedee9e50ec3b9e614b2b192d3f","tid":1973872,"uid":271187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"香港電台 OK.<br />\n其他太假, 不了."},{"pid":"d309cdafef1e86993efecab9a9d57117d7999f29","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"大家醒一醒，我地既敵人 唔係黃絲 唔係黃店 唔係黃媒，而係一個極權"},{"pid":"ae547f822b103bd5a73c880faa581cae79d54256","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d4b3fdb75d08f8e6eb0b0fc96295a57d4728270","tid":1973872,"uid":270768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a833fa90cb9e29e5bda0aa9df908f528568d58bf","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"請大家勿忘初衷"},{"pid":"9f6c21af38073bd32fe8c1e1f663496595b3e657","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"極權已經摧毀左我地好多野"},{"pid":"f65172d7e45c34923c3701b4a25bdba30e62a69d","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"武肺過後，大家一定要繼續走出黎"},{"pid":"84411c087d2dea7606c760db105ca938bf2fac52","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭 黑警 中共 奶共 死全家"},{"pid":"7a523c891b87847be77a498fb8fc203f945647c1","tid":1973872,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"所以大家訂閱蕭生啦<br />\n<br />\n都只係35蚊左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再分享出去"},{"pid":"e1cd9a161546a4089b9283c2d6ee496def31b0cc","tid":1973872,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"通常分化撚第一句就會笠頂高帽比人戴先<br />\n<br />\n例如龍門單嘢就會話：連登唔講得龍門壞話㗎/龍衛兵/你講龍門會比人話你分化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後先擋咗班叫人唔好分化嘅人出聲，自己再慢慢分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完上一頁<br />\n<br />\n如果間黃店我真係覺得有問題，我自己選擇唔幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8319ef2177be9d45b76f486a2a13aefa5b1d73f5","tid":1973872,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1cd9a161546a4089b9283c2d6ee496def31b0cc","tid":1973872,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"通常分化撚第一句就會笠頂高帽比人戴先<br />\n<br />\n例如龍門單嘢就會話：連登唔講得龍門壞話㗎/龍衛兵/你講龍門會比人話你分化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後先擋咗班叫人唔好分化嘅人出聲，自己再慢慢分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完上一頁<br />\n<br />\n如果間黃店我真係覺得有問題，我自己選擇唔幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"諗住出去搵個post 唔小心覆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍門單嘢大家記唔記得最後係搵咗東週po, 而事主嘅原因係因為蘋果唔肯報道<br />\n<br />\n如果佢真係分化撚，證明而家對家嘅技巧係有後續發展，多咗support，令到件事更真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於有手足現身屌7龍門饅頭張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1971144\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1971144</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f58dea73b677d4f936a87643d6ff28b5d39b9a4","tid":1973872,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81a34f5633005b56b1d0387ce1b7f98c71bb871","tid":1973872,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-1